    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Before Combat </b>The wizard casts <i>mage armor</i>.<br/><b>During Combat </b>The wizard uses hand of the apprentice to throw her quarterstaff or casts <i>burning hands</i>. She offers to use her <i>scroll of enlarge person </i>on an ally who\u2019ll protect her.<br/><b>Base Statistics </b>Without <i>mage armor</i>, the wizard\u2019s statistics are <b>AC </b>11, touch 11, flat-footed 10."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "These mages are new adventurers looking for protectors."
